      • convert

        public Channel convert(Channel channel,
                       ConversionPolicy changeExisting)
        Converts channelIn to have voxels with data-type T.

        This can occur by either replacing the existing voxels in the channel, or creating a new channel entirely.

        Parameters:
        channel - channel whose voxels will be converted.
        changeExisting - if true, the contents of the existing channel will be changed with the new type, if false, rather a new channel will be created.
        Returns:
